org.gearvrf

Class GVRMaterialShaderId

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gearvrf.GVRShaderId
      • org.gearvrf.GVRMaterialShaderId
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GVRCustomMaterialShaderId, GVRStockMaterialShaderId

    public abstract class GVRMaterialShaderId
extends GVRShaderId
    Opaque type that specifies a material shader. Currently material and post effect shaders are kept in separate realms. Material shader IDs may overlap PostEffect shader IDs.
